channel.title: What to do in RS?
channel.description:
Well, I have a lvl 84 main that i recently recovered, found out it got hacked, has members until jan 20th, and around 600k cash.
Some of my stats are.
70 att 70 str 63 def 89 mage 99 fishing 99 thieving 95 cooking
and I was wondering what I could do for $ that is fun. Since im pretty poor.
Also I have dt done
edit: shiz I might have a give away for this account if a mod would be so ever kind to approve it :) and take off my moderation so I can reply to people fast XD (just for the time being :3)

item.dc:creator: @Mitko Mitko
item.description:
@Mitko wrote:

[quote=“Wet Dreamss, post:9, topic:428517”][quote author=Mitko link=topic=531209.msg3881380#msg3881380 date=1326055791]
Use that 99 thieving to pickpocket the farmers, seen a few guides on YouTube about it, not sure how the prices are now though.

Also with 99 fishing you could fish some rocktails and relax, watch some TV, movies and stuff. :o Their price is quite high now.
[/quote]
ill probably fish some rocks for a lil bit, but I can’t really relax while fishing them cuz the rock people attack you :#

edit: super slow. Only caught 15 in about 10-20 minutes. lol[/quote]Yeah they’re quite slow to catch, I usually take with me around 5 granite lobster pouches to boost the fishing a bit. Also rock creatures shouldn’t be a problem if you are on w84.

item.description:
